## Development

### Python

```bash
poetry install

poetry run pytest

poetry run pytest --ignore=maplibre/ipywidget.py --doctest-modules maplibre
```

### JavaScript

See [maplibre-bindings](https://github.com/eoda-dev/maplibre-bindings)

